          "speaker_gender": "Male"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「そうなれば、私たちは家族として共に死ぬことになりますね」",
      "modification_date": "2024-06-24T19:25:17.7976518Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2024-06-24T19:25:17.7976521Z",
      "original_text": "\"In that case, we will die together as a family.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2024-06-24T19:25:17.7976536Z",
          "locale_text": "「そうなれば、私たちは家族として共に死ぬことになりますね」",
          "speaker": "MasterInfernus",
          "speaker_gender": "Male"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“既然如此，我和我的家人们可以死在一起了。”",
      "modification_date": "2024-06-24T19:26:50.0911430Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2024-06-24T19:26:50.0911433Z",
      "original_text": "\"In that case, we will die together as a family.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2024-06-24T19:26:50.0911447Z",
          "locale_text": "“既然如此，我和我的家人们可以死在一起了。”",
          "speaker": "MasterInfernus",
          "speaker_gender": "Male"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Dann werden wir als Familie zusammen sterben.\"",
      "modification_date": "2024-07-15T11:50:55.8906072Z",
